   <talk_paragraph index="n1603_juergen-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1603_juergen-2-b" mid="34" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Undercover Spy$<BR>When I was still an apprentice spy, my master told me something. He said there's nothing worse than getting caught, because once your identity is revealed, no one can help you, not even your fellow spies, or else they'll get caught, too. He knew about it firsthand, because it happened to his best friends... <FONT color=#a94407>Lena's</FONT> parents.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1603_juergen-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1603_juergen-2-c" mid="35" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>No way... General Douglas did that?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Undercover Spy$<BR>my master also told me that their daughter ended up being raised by the one who left them to die. That means... Lena's current father, General Douglas, is actually the enemy who let her parents die.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1603_juergen-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1603_juergen-2-d" mid="36" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I see.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Undercover Spy$<BR>The best way to find out the truth would be to ask General Douglas.<BR>The leader of the Dragon Followers who killed Lena's parents died in a recent battle too... so that's the only chance.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1603_juergen-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1603_juergen-2-e" mid="37" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Before you go, can you tell me your name?</html>]]></talk_answer>
